channel.title: A collab but it's a competition between every group of only 2 people
channel.description:
I was just listening to the newest featured song when this idea struck me. Here's how it will go: We will be divided into however many groups of 2 we can get. The 2 should be able to communicate using any sort of messaging or video chat website or app (Twitter, Kik, anything you can message with). I say they should be done by the end of September. I will not compete so find somebody who needs a fellow Auxian to make their collab. Good luck!
Update: Post it to SoundCloud as the name: 2vsAll Collab Competition.
Update 2: This contest has been cancelled for further notice.
